snippet.title: Emily in Paris: Netflix Stories | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Say “oui” to possibility. Follow your heart and live out your own story set in the City of Love in this interactive story based on the hit series.

Play Emily In Paris: Netflix Stories on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81774710

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
